<h1>Pizza finder</h1>
<h4>We will help find you pizza using the Foursquare API!</h4>

<p>Please allow this site access to your location.</p>
<p>Lookup will take a few seconds after you allow access.</p>
<p>This site will default to the address of Peet's coffee in Berkeley, CA if location access is not allowed.</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Latitude:</strong> {{lat}}</li>
    <li><strong>Longituge: </strong>{{long}}</li>
    <li><strong>Formatted Address: </strong>{{address}}</li>
</ul>

<p>Results will be shown below once available:</p>

{{#each places as |place|}}
<ul class='pizza-list'>
    <li class='pizza-list-item'><strong>{{place.name}}</strong></li>
    <li class='pizza-list-item'>{{place.address}}</li>
    <li class='pizza-list-item'><a href='tel:+1{{place.phone}}'>{{place.formattedPhone}}</a></li>
</ul>
{{/each}}

{{yield}}
